\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 You all may know me as a governnor of the river cities. General in times of conflict. }
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 I\loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8217\'92ve seen you burn Viallges.}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 You can\loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8217\'92t blame me for that! Because we are governors, yes, generals, yes, but mostly we are slaves.}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 If you are looking for sympathy among the aryamun, perhaps you should keep in mind that not two days ago, you disintigrated thirty of our number.}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 Forgive me. The subtlety ofhuman expression is a difficult}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 Relax. This is your deal. You are in control. There are just some questions that I would really, really like to know the answers to. I will cooperate fully if you tell me. }
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 You dont have a choice to cooperate.}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 I think you\loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8217\'92ve mistaken me for a creature that fears for its life.}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 How did you explode that corpse in such a way as to split rock.}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 I didn\loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8217\'92t do it, elrahet did.}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 How did you bring mandrameen back to life?}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 I didn\loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8217\'92t do it, Elrahed did.}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 Elrahet. Elrahet. I didn\loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8217\'92t ask who did it, I asked how.}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 Even if I told you, I\loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8217\'92m sure you\u8217\'92ll ask more questions of clarification, after which ill have to have told the history of the universe until it came to be. No, for now, you\u8217\'92ll settle with Elrahet did it.}
